sep.gaia.state

Interface AbstractStateManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StateManager

    public interface AbstractStateManager
    Interface to manage the different categories of states by updating all states whenever one of them is changed. An implementing class has to be a Singleton.
    Author:
    Max Witzelsperger

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes

      static class  AbstractStateManager.StateType
      Enumerates all possible types of concrete states to be managed.
